View the average Azuki Collector points per Eth for all Azuki NFTs.  

Azuki NFTs each have an arbitrary point value assigned for collectors found on azuki.com and azuki.com/gallery.  This point value is created by the Azuki team and not attached to details on the Blur NFT marketplace.  This plugin has all the recent collector point values associated with all three Azuki collections (Azuki, Azuki Elementals, and Beanz) and calculates the average number of points per Eth depending on the price for each NFT.  On any of the three Azuki marketplaces on Blur, this app will calculate and overlay the price per item over the profile so that manual calculations of any of the total 49950 NFTs don't have to be manually checked each time (by cross referencing the point value on Azuki.com).
